parts.text:
```json
{
"application": "PBS",
"details": {
"software": [
"felixsim",
"felixrefine"
],
"resources": {
"nodes": "Number of nodes to use for the job",
"wtime": "Maximum wall clock time for the job",
"processes": "Number of processes to run the simulation with",
"ranks": "Number of MPI ranks to use for the job",
"taskspernode": "Number of tasks per node",
"mppwidth": "Width of the MPI process grid",
"submitdir": "Directory to submit the job from",
"bashtmpdir": "Temporary directory to run the simulation in",
"inputfiledir": "Directory containing the input files",
"binarydir": "Directory containing the felixsim/refine executables"
},
"other": {
"Job_Name": "Name of the job",
"cores": "Number of cores to use for the job",
"dummyprocesses": "Default number of processes, calculated from the number of cores",
"job_dir": "Directory to store the job files",
"job_file": "Name of the job file",
"targetdir": "Directory to store the output files"
}
}
}
```
